e^z = \lim \limits_{x \rightarrow \infty} \left( 1 + \frac{z}{x} \right)^x
e = \lim \limits_{x \rightarrow \infty} \left( 1 + \frac{1}{x} \right)^x
y=x/z
 \lim \limits_{x \rightarrow \infty} \left( 1 + \frac{z}{x} \right)^x = \lim \limits_{y \rightarrow \infty} \left( 1 + \frac{1}{y} \right)^{yz} = \left(\lim \limits_{y \rightarrow \infty} \left( 1 + \frac{1}{y} \right)^{y}\right)^z  = e^z 
a^x
a^{xy}=(a^x)^y
x\mapsto a^x
